OL,3,CStruggling council permitted to hike
OL,4,Ccouncil tax by nearly nine per cent
OL,6,FStruggling North Somerset Council has
OL,7,Fbeen granted special permission by the
OL,8,Fgovernment to raise council tax by
OL,9,F8.99 per cent from April, almost
OL,10,Fdouble the capped 4.99 per cent annual
OL,11,Fincrease.
OL,13,FThe council had initially requested
OL,14,Fpermission to raise the tax by 10 per
OL,15,Fcent, warning that without
OL,16,F"exceptional financial support" it
OL,17,Fcould be forced to issue a section 114
OL,18,Fnotice, making it effectively bankrupt.
