OL,3,CStruggling council permitted to hike
OL,4,Ccouncil tax by nearly nine per cent
OL,6,FCouncil leader Mike Bell says the
OL,7,Fcouncil was one of just seven across
OL,8,Fthe country permitted to raise council
OL,9,Ftax above the usual limit on Monday, 9
OL,10,FFebruary, demonstrating the "severity"
OL,11,Fof its financial situation.
OL,13,F"None of us wants to raise council tax
OL,14,Fbeyond the usual limits, but our
OL,15,Ffinancial position has worsened, and
OL,16,Fdemand and cost pressures have
OL,17,Fincreased every year since 2010," he
OL,18,Fsaid.
