OL,3,CStruggling council permitted to hike
OL,4,Ccouncil tax by nearly nine per cent
OL,6,FCouncillors will decide whether or not
OL,7,Fthey will impose the 8.99 per cent tax
OL,8,Fincrease at their annual budget
OL,9,Fsetting meeting on Tuesday, 24
OL,10,FFebruary.
OL,12,FThe increase would mean those living
OL,13,Fin Band D properties in North Somerset
OL,14,Fwill see their bills increase by
OL,15,F#13.44 a month.
OL,17,FThis amounts to an extra #161.28 per
OL,18,Fyear.
