OL,3,CStruggling council permitted to hike
OL,4,Ccouncil tax by nearly nine per cent
OL,6,FIn October 2025, the council warned it
OL,7,Ffaced a budget shortfall of
OL,8,F#25.9million.
OL,10,FMajor savings plans have reduced that
OL,11,Fposition to #8.4million, but that must
OL,12,Fbe brought to zero by the budget
OL,13,Fdeadline on 11 March 2026.
OL,15,FA spokesperson for North Somerset
OL,16,FCouncil said that even with additional
OL,17,Fcouncil tax income, an additional
OL,18,F#2.4million of savings will need to be
OL,19,Fmade to balance the budget.
OL,21,FWhat is a section 114 notice?
