OL,3,CStruggling council permitted to hike
OL,4,Ccouncil tax by nearly nine per cent
OL,6,FBecause councils provide essential
OL,7,Fservices, they cannot declare
OL,8,Fbankruptcy in the way that a business
OL,9,Fcan.
OL,11,FInstead, if they cannot set a balanced
OL,12,Fbudget for a year, they must issue a
OL,13,Fsection 114 notice.
OL,15,FThis effectively declares bankruptcy
OL,16,Fand forces a council to slash all non-
OL,17,Fessential spending.
OL,19,FJust 17 section 114 notices have ever
OL,20,Fbeen issued by councils, 11 of which
OL,21,Fhave been since 2018.
